rush edit - Edit package files

Alias: e

Usage:
  rush edit PACKAGE [FILE]
  rush edit --help | -h

Options:
  --help, -h
    Show this help

Arguments:
  PACKAGE
    Package name.
    This can either be the package name without the repository name (in
    this case, the default repository will be used) or in the form of
    'repo:package'.

  FILE
    File to edit.
    Default: main
